menus.controller

Class GameInfoController

  • java.lang.Object
    • menus.controller.Controller
      • menus.controller.GameInfoController

  • public class GameInfoController
extends Controller
    controller class for Game Info scene. Sets up the scene layout, buttons, paddings etc. Uses images and texts to show information about how to play the game, as well as show images whose function serves as a game tutorial.
    See Also:
    Image
